<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Account Already Registered</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,sans-serif;line-height:1.5;color:#333;max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 20px;">
  <h2 style="margin:0 0 24px 0;font-weight:600;">You already have an account</h2>
  <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;">Hi {{name}},</p>
  <p style="margin:0 0 24px 0;">
    Someone just tried to register with this email address. If that was you,
    you already have an account — log in below.
  </p>
  <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 24px;background-color:#2563eb;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;font-weight:500;">Log in to your account</a>
  <p style="margin:24px 0 0 0;font-size:14px;color:#666;">
    If you did not attempt to register, you can safely ignore this email.
    Your account remains secure.
  </p>
</body>
</html>
